# Financial Risk Market Daily Loss Fourth Largest Amount

## identifier
de8050

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of the fourth largest daily loss experienced by the reporting party over the relevant period due to market movements.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Market.DailyLossFourthLargest.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=duration
